lead_paragraph: Andrew Svoboda rallied to win the Web.com Tour's Brazil Champions on Sunday, closing with a birdie to overcome a one-stroke deficit to Bhavik Patel.

headline.print_headline: Andrew Svoboda Wins Web.com Tour's Brazil Champions
